630246,126,1332,2,6,1,40,4,Sattatantiṃ sumadhuran ti guttilavimānaṃ. 
630247,126,1332,7,10,1,16,3,Tassa kā uppatti? 
630248,126,1332,11,50,1,343,34,Bhagavati rājagahe viharante āyasmā mahāmoggallāno heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva devacārikaṃ caranto tāvatiṃsabhavanaṃ gantvā tattha paṭipāṭiyā ṭhitesu chattiṃsāya vimānesu chattiṃsa devadhītaro paccekaṃ accharāsahassaparivārā mahatiṃ dibbasampattiṃ anubhavantiyo disvā tāhi pubbe katakammaṃ‘‘ abhikkantena vaṇṇenā’’ tiādīhi tīhi gāthāhi paṭipāṭiyā pucchi. 
630249,126,1332,51,62,1,68,7,Tāpi tassa pucchānantaraṃ‘‘ vatthuttamadāyikā nārī’’ tiādinā byākariṃsu. 
630250,126,1332,63,71,1,65,8,Atha thero tato manussalokaṃ āgantvā bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
630251,126,1332,72,106,1,194,28,"Taṃ sutvā bhagavā‘‘ moggallāna, tā devatā na kevalaṃ tayā eva pucchitā evaṃ byākariṃsu, atha kho pubbe mayāpi pucchitā evameva byākariṃsū’’ ti vatvā therena yācito atītaṃ attano guttilācariyaṃ kathesi. "
630252,126,1333,2,23,1,197,19,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto gandhabbakule nibbattitvā gandhabbasippe pariyodātasippatāya timbarunāradasadiso sabbadisāsu pākaṭo paññātā ācariyo ahosi nāmena guttilo nāma. 
630253,126,1333,24,29,1,32,5,So andhe jiṇṇe mātāpitaro posesi. 
630254,126,1333,30,61,1,167,23,Tassa sippanipphattiṃ sutvā ujjenivāsī musilo nāma gandhabbo upagantvā taṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ ṭhito‘‘ kasmā āgatosī’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ tumhākaṃ santike sippaṃ uggaṇhitun’’ ti āha. 
630255,126,1333,62,84,1,160,17,"Guttilācariyo taṃ oloketvā lakkhaṇakusalatāya‘‘ ayaṃ puriso visamajjhāsayo kakkhaḷo pharuso akataññū bhavissati, na saṅgahetabbo’’ ti sippuggahaṇatthaṃ okāsaṃ nākāsi. "
630256,126,1333,85,91,1,47,6,So tassa mātāpitaro payirupāsitvā tehi yācāpesi. 
630257,126,1333,92,113,1,180,17,Guttilācariyo mātāpitūhi nippīḷiyamāno‘‘ garuvacanaṃ alaṅghanīyan’’ ti tassa sippaṃ paṭṭhapetvā vigatamacchariyatāya kāruṇikatāya ca ācariyamuṭṭhiṃ akatvā anavasesato sippaṃ sikkhāpesi. 
630258,126,1334,2,35,1,243,27,"Sopi medhāvitāya pubbekataparicayatāya akusītatāya ca na cirasseva pariyodātasippo hutvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ bārāṇasī jambudīpe agganagaraṃ, yaṃnūnāhaṃ idha sarājikāya parisāya sippaṃ dasseyyaṃ, evāhaṃ ācariyatopi jambudīpe pākaṭo paññāto bhavissāmī’’ ti. "
630259,126,1334,36,53,1,82,12,"So ācariyassa ārocesi‘‘ ahaṃ rañño purato sippaṃ dassetukāmo, rājānaṃ maṃ dassethā’’ ti. "
630260,126,1334,54,84,1,166,22,Mahāsatto‘‘ ayaṃ mama santike uggahitasippo patiṭṭhaṃ labhatū’’ ti karuṇāyamāno taṃ rañño santikaṃ netvā‘‘ mahārāja imassa me antevāsikassa vīṇāya paguṇataṃ passathā’’ ti āha. 
630261,126,1334,85,114,1,157,20,"Rājā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā tassa vīṇāvādanaṃ sutvā parituṭṭho taṃ gantukāmaṃ nivāretvā‘‘ mameva santike vasa, ācariyassa dinnakoṭṭhāsato upaḍḍhaṃ dassāmī’’ ti āha. "
630262,126,1334,115,184,1,344,48,"Musilo‘‘ nāhaṃ ācariyato hāyāmi, samameva dethā’’ ti vatvā raññā‘‘ mā evaṃ bhaṇi, ācariyo nāma mahanto, upaḍḍhameva tuyhaṃ dassāmī’’ ti vutte‘‘ mama ca ācariyassa ca sippaṃ passathā’’ ti vatvā rājagehato nikkhamitvā‘‘ ito sattame divase mama ca guttilācariyassa ca rājaṅgaṇe sippadassanaṃ bhavissati, taṃ passitukāmā passantū’’ ti tattha tattha āhiṇḍanto ugghosesi. "
