632268,126,2483,2,34,1,269,27,Evaṃ bhagavatā tīhi gāthāhi saraṇaguṇasandassanena saddhiṃ saraṇagamanavidhimhi vutte māṇavo taṃtaṃsaraṇaguṇānussaraṇamukhena saraṇagamanavidhino attano hadaye ṭhapitabhāvaṃ vibhāvento tassā tassā gāthāya anantaraṃ‘‘ yo vadataṃ pavaro’’ tiādinā taṃ taṃ gāthaṃ paccanubhāsi. 
632269,126,2483,35,47,1,115,12,Evaṃ paccanubhāsitvā ṭhitassa pañca sikkhāpadāni sarūpato phalānisaṃsato ca vibhāvetvā tesaṃ samādānavidhiṃ kathesi. 
632270,126,2483,48,67,1,131,15,So tampi suṭṭhu upadhāretvā pasannamānaso‘‘ handāhaṃ bhagavā gamissāmī’’ ti vatvā ratanattayaguṇaṃ anussaranto taṃyeva maggaṃ paṭipajji. 
632271,126,2483,68,81,1,79,9,Bhagavāpi‘‘ alaṃ imassa ettakaṃ kusalaṃ devalokūpapattiyā’’ ti jetavanameva agamāsi. 
632272,126,2484,2,34,1,278,27,"Māṇavassa pana pasannacittassa ratanattayaguṇaṃ sallakkhaṇavasena‘‘ saraṇaṃ upemī’’ ti pavattacittuppādatāya saraṇesu ca, bhagavatā vuttanayena pañcannaṃ sīlānaṃ adhiṭṭhānena sīlesu ca patiṭṭhitassa teneva nayena ratanattayaguṇe anussarantasseva gacchantassa corā magge pariyuṭṭhiṃsu. "
632273,126,2484,35,41,1,55,6,So te agaṇetvā ratanattayaguṇe anussarantoyeva gacchati. 
632274,126,2484,42,60,1,158,17,Tañceko coro gumbantaraṃ upanissāya ṭhito visapītena sarena sahasāva vijjhitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā kahāpaṇabhaṇḍikaṃ gahetvā attano sahāyehi saddhiṃ pakkāmi. 
632275,126,2484,61,81,1,228,19,"Māṇavo pana kālaṃ katvā tāvatiṃsabhavane tiṃsayojanike kanakavimāne suttappabuddho viya accharāsahassaparivuto saṭṭhisakaṭabhārālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitattabhāvo nibbatti, tassa vimānassa ābhā sātirekāni vīsatiyojanāni pharitvā tiṭṭhati. "
632276,126,2485,2,20,1,164,17,Atha māṇavaṃ kālakataṃ disvā setabyagāmavāsino manussā setabyaṃ gantvā tassa mātāpitūnaṃ ukkaṭṭhagāmavāsino ca ukkaṭṭhaṃ gantvā brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa kathesuṃ. 
632277,126,2485,21,47,1,212,24,"Taṃ sutvā tassa mātāpitaro ñātimittā brāhmaṇo ca pokkharasāti saparivārā assumukhā rodamānā taṃ padesaṃ agamaṃsu, yebhuyyena setabyavāsino ca ukkaṭṭhavāsino ca icchānaṅgalavāsino ca sannipatiṃsu, mahāsamāgamo ahosi. "
