634440,126,3705,21,38,1,128,13,Brāhmaṇopi kho bhagavati sañjātapasādabahumāno devatāya ca codiyamāno‘‘ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ upasaṅkamissāmī’’ ti vihārābhimukho gacchati. 
634441,126,3705,39,64,1,158,20,"Taṃ disvā mahājano‘‘ ayaṃ brāhmaṇo ettakaṃ kālaṃ tathāgataṃ anupasaṅkamitvā ajja puttasokena upasaṅkamati, kīdisī nu kho dhammadesanā bhavissatī’’ ti taṃ anubandhi. "
