635025,127,33,2,15,1,114,12,Taṃ panetaṃ vatthuṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharanto veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe aññataraṃ seṭṭhiputtapetaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
635026,127,33,16,26,1,106,10,Rājagahe kira aññataro aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo pahūtavittūpakaraṇo anekakoṭidhanasannicayo seṭṭhi ahosi. 
635027,127,33,27,37,1,63,6,Tassa mahādhanasampannatāya‘‘ mahādhanaseṭṭhi’’ tveva samaññā ahosi. 
635028,127,33,38,44,1,29,5,"Ekova putto ahosi, piyo manāpo. "
635029,127,33,45,51,1,46,6,Tasmiṃ viññutaṃ patte mātāpitaro evaṃ cintesuṃ–
635030,127,33,52,83,1,238,25,"‘‘ amhākaṃ puttassa divase divase sahassaṃ sahassaṃ paribbayaṃ karontassa vassasatenāpi ayaṃ dhanasannicayo parikkhayaṃ na gamissati, kiṃ imassa sippuggahaṇaparissamena, akilantakāyacitto yathāsukhaṃ bhoge paribhuñjatū’’ ti sippaṃ na sikkhāpesuṃ. "
635031,127,33,84,91,1,94,7,Vayappatte pana kularūpayobbanavilāsasampannaṃ kāmābhimukhaṃ dhammasaññāvimukhaṃ kaññaṃ ānesuṃ. 
635032,127,33,92,149,1,498,51,"So tāya saddhiṃ abhiramanto dhamme cittamattampi anuppādetvā, samaṇabrāhmaṇagurujanesu anādaro hutvā, dhuttajanaparivuto rajjamāno pañcakāmaguṇe rato giddho mohena andho hutvā kālaṃ vītināmetvā, mātāpitūsu kālakatesu naṭanāṭakagāyakādīnaṃ yathicchitaṃ dento dhanaṃ vināsetvā nacirasseva pārijuññappatto hutvā, iṇaṃ gahetvā jīvikaṃ kappento puna iṇampi alabhitvā iṇāyikehi codiyamāno tesaṃ attano khettavatthugharādīni datvā, kapālahattho bhikkhaṃ caritvā bhuñjanto tasmiṃyeva nagare anāthasālāyaṃ vasati. "
635033,127,34,2,8,1,44,6,Atha naṃ ekadivasaṃ corā samāgatā evamāhaṃsu–
635034,127,34,9,28,1,114,13,"‘‘ ambho purisa, kiṃ tuyhaṃ iminā dujjīvitena, taruṇo tvamasi thāmajavabalasampanno, kasmā hatthapādavikalo viya acchasi? "
635035,127,34,29,42,1,76,11,Ehi amhehi saha corikāya paresaṃ santakaṃ gahetvā sukhena jīvikaṃ kappehī’’ ti. 
635036,127,34,43,54,1,36,7,So‘‘ nāhaṃ corikaṃ kātuṃ jānāmī’’ ti āha. 
635037,127,34,55,71,1,71,11,"Corā‘‘ mayaṃ taṃ sikkhāpema, kevalaṃ tvaṃ amhākaṃ vacanaṃ karohī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
635038,127,34,72,83,1,47,7,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā tehi saddhiṃ agamāsi. 
635039,127,34,84,100,1,116,16,Atha te corā tassa hatthe mahantaṃ muggaraṃ datvā sandhiṃ chinditvā gharaṃ pavisanto taṃ sandhimukhe ṭhapetvā āhaṃsu–
635040,127,34,101,118,1,84,12,"‘‘ sace idha añño koci āgacchati, taṃ iminā muggarena paharitvā ekappahāreneva mārehī’’ ti. "
635041,127,34,119,129,1,75,9,So andhabālo hitāhitaṃ ajānanto paresaṃ āgamanameva olokento tattha aṭṭhāsi . 
635042,127,34,130,143,1,102,13,Corā pana gharaṃ pavisitvā gayhūpagaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ gahetvā gharamanussehi ñātamattāva ito cito ca palāyiṃsu. 
635043,127,34,144,171,1,178,23,Gharamanussā uṭṭhahitvā sīghaṃ sīghaṃ dhāvantā ito cito ca olokentā taṃ purisaṃ sandhidvāre ṭhitaṃ disvā‘‘ hare duṭṭhacorā’’ ti gahetvā hatthapāde muggarādīhi pothetvā rañño dassesuṃ–
635044,127,34,172,184,1,36,6,"‘‘ ayaṃ, deva, coro sandhisukhe gahito’’ ti. "
635045,127,34,185,196,1,54,7,Rājā‘‘ imassa sīsaṃ chindāpehī’’ ti nagaraguttikaṃ āṇāpesi.
635046,127,34,197,223,1,264,21,"‘‘ Sādhu, devā’’ ti nagaraguttiko taṃ gāhāpetvā pacchābāhaṃ gāḷhabandhanaṃ bandhāpetvā rattavaṇṇaviraḷamālābandhakaṇṭhaṃ iṭṭhakacuṇṇamakkhitasīsaṃ vajjhapahaṭabheridesitamaggaṃ rathikāya rathikaṃ siṅghāṭakena siṅghāṭakaṃ vicarāpetvā kasāhi tāḷento āghātanābhimukhaṃ neti."
635047,127,34,224,236,1,63,8,‘‘ Ayaṃ imasmiṃ nagare vilumpamānakacoro gahito’’ ti kolāhalaṃ ahosi. 
635048,127,35,2,46,1,309,39,Tena ca samayena tasmiṃ nagare sulasā nāma nagarasobhinī pāsāde ṭhitā vātapānantarena olokentī taṃ tathā nīyamānaṃ disvā pubbe tena kataparicayā‘‘ ayaṃ puriso imasmiṃyeva nagare mahatiṃ sampattiṃ anubhavitvā idāni evarūpaṃ anatthaṃ anayabyasanaṃ patto’’ ti tassa kāruññaṃ uppādetvā cattāro modake pānīyañca pesesi. 
635049,127,35,47,50,1,29,3,Nagaraguttikassa ca ārocāpesi–
635050,127,35,51,68,1,73,11,"‘‘ tāva ayyo āgametu, yāvāyaṃ puriso ime modake khāditvā pānīyaṃ pivissatī’’ ti. "
635051,127,36,2,14,1,117,12,Athetasmiṃ antare āyasmā mahāmoggallāno dibbena cakkhunā olokento tassa byasanappattiṃ disvā karuṇāya sañcoditamānaso–
635052,127,36,15,50,1,239,28,"‘‘ ayaṃ puriso akatapuñño katapāpo, tenāyaṃ niraye nibbattissati, mayi pana gate modake ca pānīyañca datvā bhummadevesu uppajjissati, yaṃnūnāhaṃ imassa avassayo bhaveyyan’’ ti cintetvā pānīyamodakesu upanīyamānesu tassa purisassa purato pāturahosi. "
635053,127,36,51,80,1,185,24,"So theraṃ disvā pasannamānaso‘‘ kiṃ me idāneva imehi māriyamānassa modakehi khāditehi, idaṃ pana paralokaṃ gacchantassa pātheyyaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti cintetvā modake ca pānīyañca therassa dāpesi. "
635054,127,36,81,95,1,139,14,Thero tassa pasādasaṃvaḍḍhanatthaṃ tassa passantasseva tathārūpe ṭhāne nisīditvā modake paribhuñjitvā pānīyañca pivitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi. 
635055,127,36,96,131,1,269,31,So pana puriso coraghātakehi āghātanaṃ netvā sīsacchedaṃ pāpito anuttare puññakkhette mahāmoggallānatthere katena puññena uḷāre devaloke nibbattanārahopi yasmā‘‘ sulasaṃ āgamma mayā ayaṃ deyyadhammo laddho’’ ti sulasāya gatena sinehena maraṇakāle cittaṃ upakkiliṭṭhaṃ ahosi. 
635056,127,36,132,141,1,108,9,Tasmā hīnakāyaṃ upapajjanto pabbatagahanasambhūte sandacchāye mahānigrodharukkhe rukkhadevatā hutvā nibbatti. 
635057,127,37,2,22,1,147,16,"So kira sace paṭhamavaye kulavaṃsaṭṭhapane ussukkaṃ akarissa, tasmiṃyeva nagare seṭṭhīnaṃ aggo abhavissa, majjhimavaye majjhimo, pacchimavaye pacchimo. "
635058,127,37,23,41,1,135,15,"Sace pana paṭhamavaye pabbajito abhavissa, arahā abhavissa, majjhimavaye sakadāgāmī anāgāmī vā abhavissa, pacchimavaye sotāpanno abhavissa. "
635059,127,37,42,55,1,147,13,Pāpamittasaṃsaggena pana itthidhutto surādhutto duccaritanirato anādariko hutvā anukkamena sabbasampattito parihāyitvā mahābyasanaṃ pattoti vadanti. 
635060,127,38,2,26,1,171,21,"Atha so aparena samayena sulasaṃ uyyānagataṃ disvā sañjātakāmarāgo andhakāraṃ māpetvā taṃ attano bhavanaṃ netvā sattāhaṃ tāya saddhiṃ saṃvāsaṃ kappesi, attānañcassā ārocesi. "
635061,127,38,27,36,1,58,9,Tassā mātā taṃ apassantī rodamānā ito cito ca paribbhamati. 
635062,127,38,37,57,1,118,15,"Taṃ disvā mahājano‘‘ ayyo mahāmoggallāno mahiddhiko mahānubhāvo tassā gatiṃ jāneyya, taṃ upasaṅkamitvā puccheyyāsī’’ ti āha. "
635063,127,38,58,70,1,54,8,Sā‘‘ sādhu ayyo’’ ti theraṃ upasaṅkamitvā tamatthaṃ pucchi. 
635064,127,38,71,87,1,103,12,Thero‘‘ ito sattame divase veḷuvanamahāvihāre bhagavati dhammaṃ desente parisapariyante passissasī’’ ti āha. 
635065,127,38,88,93,1,32,5,Atha sulasā taṃ devaputtaṃ avoca–
635066,127,38,94,123,1,146,20,"‘‘ ayuttaṃ mayhaṃ tava bhavane vasantiyā, ajja sattamo divaso, mama mātā maṃ apassantī paridevasokasamāpannā bhavissati, sādhu maṃ, deva, tattheva nehī’’ ti. "
