635087,127,49,2,18,1,120,11,"1. Tattha {khettūpamā}ti khittaṃ vuttaṃ bījaṃ tāyati mahapphalabhāvakaraṇena rakkhatīti khettaṃ, sālibījādīnaṃ viruhanaṭṭhānaṃ. "
