635169,127,71,112,132,1,159,18,"Sace pana tvaṃ mukharo hutvā vācāya pāpaṃ kareyyāsi, ekaṃsena sūkaramukho bhaveyyāsi, tasmā mākāsi mukhasā pāpanti phalapaṭisedhanamukhenapi hetumeva paṭisedheti. "
