637471,127,1097,42,62,1,181,19,Santappito satataṃ sadā {bahūhī}ti annapānavatthādīhi bahūhi deyyadhammehi ariyasaṅghaṃ santappentena tayā sadā sabbakālaṃ yāvajīvaṃ tatthāpi satataṃ nirantaraṃ ahaṃ santappito pīṇito. 
637472,127,1097,63,83,1,120,15,Yāmi ahaṃ sukhito {manussadevā}ti‘‘ tasmā ahaṃ idāni sukhito manussadeva mahārāja yathicchitaṭṭhānaṃ yāmī’’ ti rājānaṃ āpucchi. 
