637477,127,1100,2,4,1,23,2,9 . Aṅkurapetavatthuvaṇṇanā 
637478,127,1101,2,13,1,86,10,Yassa atthāya {gacchāmā}ti idaṃ satthā sāvatthiyaṃ viharanto aṅkurapetaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
637479,127,1101,14,35,1,108,15,"Kāmañcettha aṅkuro peto na hoti, tassa pana caritaṃ yasmā petasambandhaṃ, tasmā taṃ‘‘ aṅkurapetavatthū’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
637480,127,1102,2,64,1,574,58,"Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepakathā– ye te uttaramadhurādhipatino rañño mahāsāgarassa puttaṃ upasāgaraṃ paṭicca uttarāpathe kaṃsabhoge asitañjananagare mahākaṃsassa dhītuyā devagabbhāya kucchiyaṃ uppannā añjanadevī vāsudevo baladevo candadevo sūriyadevo aggidevo varuṇadevo ajjuno pajjuno ghaṭapaṇḍito aṅkuro cāti vāsudevādayo dasa bhātikāti ekādasa khattiyā ahesuṃ, tesu vāsudevādayo bhātaro asitañjananagaraṃ ādiṃ katvā dvāravatīpariyosānesu sakalajambudīpe tesaṭṭhiyā nagarasahassesu sabbe rājāno cakkena jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā dvāravatiyaṃ vasamānā rajjaṃ dasa koṭṭhāse katvā vibhajiṃsu. "
637481,127,1102,65,70,1,36,5,Bhaginiṃ pana añjanadeviṃ na sariṃsu. 
637482,127,1102,71,108,1,192,27,"Puna saritvā‘‘ ekādasa koṭṭhāse karomā’’ ti vutte tesaṃ sabbakaniṭṭho aṅkuro‘‘ mama koṭṭhāsaṃ tassā detha, ahaṃ vohāraṃ katvā jīvissāmi, tumhe attano attano janapadesu suṅkaṃ mayhaṃ vissajjethā’’ ti āha. "
637483,127,1102,109,125,1,91,12,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā tassa koṭṭhāyaṃ bhaginiyā datvā nava rājāno dvāravatiyaṃ vasiṃsu. 
637484,127,1103,2,9,1,54,7,Aṅkuro pana vaṇijjaṃ karonto niccakālaṃ mahādānaṃ deti. 
637485,127,1103,10,17,1,46,6,Tassa paneko dāso bhaṇḍāgāriko atthakāmo ahosi. 
637486,127,1103,18,25,1,58,7,Aṅkuro pasannamānaso tassa ekaṃ kuladhītaraṃ gahetvā adāsi. 
637487,127,1103,26,30,1,34,4,So putte gabbhagateyeva kālamakāsi. 
637488,127,1103,31,40,1,64,9,Aṅkuro tasmiṃ jāte tassa pituno dinnaṃ bhattavetanaṃ tassa adāsi. 
637489,127,1103,41,56,1,73,11,Atha tasmiṃ dārake vayappatte‘‘ dāso na dāso’’ ti rājakule vinicchayo uppajji. 
637490,127,1103,57,74,1,94,13,Taṃ sutvā añjanadevī dhenūpamaṃ vatvā‘‘ mātu bhujissāya puttopi bhujisso evā’’ ti dāsabyato mocesi. 
637491,127,1104,2,18,1,148,16,Dārako pana lajjāya tattha vasituṃ avisahanto roruvanagaraṃ gantvā tattha aññatarassa tunnavāyassa dhītaraṃ gahetvā tunnavāyasippena jīvikaṃ kappesi. 
637492,127,1104,19,25,1,54,6,Tena samayena roruvanagare asayhamahāseṭṭhi nāma ahosi. 
637493,127,1104,26,30,1,62,4,So samaṇabrāhmaṇakapaṇaddhikavanibbakayācakānaṃ mahādānaṃ deti. 
637494,127,1104,31,52,1,157,17,So tunnavāyo seṭṭhino gharaṃ ajānantānaṃ pītisomanassajāto hutvā asayhaseṭṭhino nivesanaṃ dakkhiṇabāhuṃ pasāretvā dassesi‘‘ ettha gantvā laddhabbaṃ labhantū’’ ti. 
637495,127,1104,53,57,1,31,4,Tassa kammaṃ pāḷiyaṃyeva āgataṃ. 
637496,127,1105,2,18,1,141,15,"So aparena samayena kālaṃ katvā marubhūmiyaṃ aññatarasmiṃ nigrodharukkhe bhummadevatā hutvā nibbatti, tassa dakkhiṇahattho sabbakāmadado ahosi. "
637497,127,1105,19,41,1,195,22,Tasmiṃyeva ca roruve aññataro puriso asayhaseṭṭhino dāne byāvaṭo assaddho appasanno micchādiṭṭhiko puññakiriyāya anādaro kālaṃ katvā tassa devaputtassa vasanaṭṭhānassa avidūre peto hutvā nibbatti. 
637498,127,1105,42,48,1,37,5,Tena ca katakammaṃ pāḷiyaṃyeva āgataṃ. 
