638098,127,1434,27,43,1,106,15,"Tena ca samayena rañño udenassa aññataro amacco kālamakāsi, tena ca pubbe nagare kammantā adhiṭṭhitā ahesuṃ. "
638099,127,1434,44,65,1,129,17,Atha rājā tassa puttaṃ uttaraṃ nāma māṇavaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ tvañca pitarā adhiṭṭhite kammante samanusāsā’’ ti tena ṭhitaṭṭhāne ṭhapesi. 
638100,127,1435,2,14,1,113,12,So ca sādhūti sampaṭicchitvā ekadivasaṃ nagarapaṭisaṅkharaṇiyānaṃ dārūnaṃ atthāya vaḍḍhakiyo gahetvā araññaṃ gato. 
