638109,127,1436,22,67,1,384,40,"Atha mahārahakappiyapaccattharaṇaatthatesu āsanesu there ca bhikkhūsu ca nisinnesu gandhapupphadhūpehi pūjaṃ katvā paṇītena annapānena te santappetvā sañjātappasādo katañjalī anumodanaṃ suṇitvā katabhattānumodane there gacchante pattaṃ gahetvā anugacchanto nagarato nikkhamitvā paṭinivattanto‘‘ bhante, tumhehi niccaṃ mama gehaṃ pavisitabban’’ ti yācitvā therassa adhivāsanaṃ ñatvā nivatti. "
