638179,127,1480,2,4,1,22,2,11 . Suttapetavatthuvaṇṇanā 
638180,127,1481,2,9,1,55,6,Ahaṃ pure pabbajitassa {bhikkhuno}ti idaṃ suttapetavatthu. 
638181,127,1481,10,13,1,16,3,Tassa kā uppatti? 
638182,127,1481,14,30,1,149,16,Sāvatthiyā kira avidūre aññatarasmiṃ gāmake amhākaṃ satthari anuppanneyeva sattannaṃ vassasatānaṃ upari aññataro dārako ekaṃ paccekabuddhaṃ upaṭṭhahi. 
638183,127,1481,31,40,1,82,9,Tassa mātā tasmiṃ vayappatte tassatthāya samānakulato aññataraṃ kuladhītaraṃ ānesi. 
638184,127,1481,41,61,1,110,14,"Vivāhadivaseyeva ca so kumāro sahāyehi saddhiṃ nhāyituṃ gato ahinā daṭṭho kālamakāsi,‘‘ yakkhagāhenā’’ tipi vadanti. "
638185,127,1481,62,80,1,159,17,"So paccekabuddhassa upaṭṭhānena bahuṃ kusalakammaṃ katvā ṭhitopi tassā dārikāya paṭibaddhacittatāya vimānapeto hutvā nibbatti, mahiddhiko pana ahosi mahānubhāvo. "
