638675,127,1710,2,15,1,90,10,Abhijjamāne {vārimhī}ti idaṃ satthari veḷuvane viharante aññataraṃ luddapetaṃ ārabbha vuttaṃ. 
638676,127,1710,16,27,1,109,11,Bārāṇasiyaṃ kira aparadisābhāge pāragaṅgāya vāsabhagāmaṃ atikkamitvā cundaṭṭhilanāmake gāme eko luddako ahosi. 
638677,127,1710,28,43,1,118,15,So araññe mige vadhitvā varamaṃsaṃ aṅgāre pacitvā khāditvā avasesaṃ paṇṇapuṭe bandhitvā kājena gahetvā gāmaṃ āgacchati. 
638678,127,1710,44,63,1,92,14,"Taṃ bāladārakā gāmadvāre disvā‘‘ maṃsaṃ me dehi, maṃsaṃ me dehī’’ ti hatthe pasāretvā upadhāvanti. "
638679,127,1710,64,70,1,34,6,So tesaṃ thokaṃ thokaṃ maṃsaṃ deti. 
638680,127,1710,71,101,1,189,24,"Athekadivasaṃ maṃsaṃ alabhitvā uddālakapupphaṃ piḷandhitvā bahuñca hatthena gahetvā gāmaṃ gacchantaṃ taṃ dārakā gāmadvāre disvā‘‘ maṃsaṃ me dehi, maṃsaṃ me dehī’’ ti hatthe pasāretvā upadhāviṃsu. "
638681,127,1710,102,107,1,36,5,So tesaṃ ekekaṃ pupphamañjariṃ adāsi. 
638682,127,1711,2,33,1,255,27,Atha aparena samayena kālaṃ katvā petesu nibbatto naggo virūparūpo bhayānakadassano supinepi annapānaṃ ajānanto sīse ābandhitauddālakakusumamālākalāpo‘‘ cundaṭṭhilāyaṃ ñātakānaṃ santike kiñci labhissāmī’’ ti gaṅgāya udake abhijjamāne paṭisotaṃ padasā gacchati. 
638683,127,1711,34,61,1,240,27,Tena ca samayena koliyo nāma rañño bimbisārassa mahāmatto kupitaṃ paccantaṃ vūpasametvā paṭinivattento hatthiassādiparivārabalaṃ thalapathena pesetvā sayaṃ gaṅgāya nadiyā anusotaṃ nāvāya āgacchanto taṃ petaṃ tathā gacchantaṃ disvā pucchanto– 
