639207,127,1967,59,88,1,184,23,"Tassa suṇisā sabbesaṃ atthāya ṭhapitamaṃsaṃ corikāya khāditvā puna tehi anuyuñjiyamānā‘‘ sace mayā taṃ maṃsaṃ khāditaṃ, bhave bhave attano piṭṭhimaṃsaṃ kantitvā khādeyyan’’ ti sapathamakāsi. "
