639211,127,1968,41,76,1,354,33,"Tassa suṇisā kammaphalena sunisitehi ativiya vipulāyatehi nakhehi attano piṭṭhimaṃsāni kantitvā khādantī aparimitaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhavati, tassa bhariyāya sugandhaṃ suvisuddhaṃ apagatakāḷakaṃ sālibhattaṃ upanītamattameva nānāvidhakimikulākulaṃ paramaduggandhajegucchaṃ gūthaṃ sampajjati, taṃ sā ubhohi hatthehi pariggahetvā bhuñjantī mahādukkhaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
