639997,127,2397,26,53,1,160,20,"‘‘ Apare pana sugatimāsamānā’’ tiādinā ca kalyāṇassa pāpassa ca kammassa vipāko vibhajitvā vutto, taṃ kinti kena kāraṇena ahaṃ avecca aparapaccayabhāvena saddaheyyaṃ. "
